AUDIENCE: I have a question
about the C6 and the C8,

00:52:59.620 --> 00:53:03.110
the chemicals that don't
break down in geological time.

00:53:03.110 --> 00:53:06.280
Does that also make
them less reactive?

00:53:06.280 --> 00:53:08.820
So would they be less
likely to cause harm

00:53:08.820 --> 00:53:12.720
in biological,
chemical reactions?

00:53:12.720 --> 00:53:14.514
ARLENE BLUM: That would be nice.

00:53:14.514 --> 00:53:15.930
AUDIENCE: Or they
just don't know?

00:53:15.930 --> 00:53:16.721
ARLENE BLUM: Right.

00:53:16.721 --> 00:53:19.390
Unfortunately, they appear
to cause a lot of harm.

00:53:19.390 --> 00:53:21.842
And the mechanisms
aren't so well known.

00:53:21.842 --> 00:53:23.800
AUDIENCE: They might be
catalysts of something?

00:53:23.800 --> 00:53:27.760
ARLENE BLUM: Yeah, or they
fit in, they fit into-- we

00:53:27.760 --> 00:53:30.430
don't know why, but there
is this unique human epi

00:53:30.430 --> 00:53:36.880
study of these 20,000
people who have been exposed

00:53:36.880 --> 00:53:38.800
in southern Ohio
and West Virginia

00:53:38.800 --> 00:53:41.550
where they came up with that
whole list of health problems

00:53:41.550 --> 00:53:43.110
that's on the slide.

00:53:43.110 --> 00:53:46.800
And in fact, that's what the
lawsuits today are starting.

00:53:46.800 --> 00:53:51.280
So it's pretty unusual to have
that much human-- because all

00:53:51.280 --> 00:53:54.300
these chemicals-- by the
way, to say the six classes,

00:53:54.300 --> 00:53:56.660
the harm is irrefutable.

00:53:56.660 --> 00:53:59.860
There are things like
genetically modified foods

00:53:59.860 --> 00:54:04.840
are a real worry, but there's
not a lot of data to show harm.

00:54:04.840 --> 00:54:06.620
What we went for
is the things where

00:54:06.620 --> 00:54:08.010
there was no question of harm.

00:54:08.010 --> 00:54:10.050
We didn't have to do
anymore experiments.

00:54:10.050 --> 00:54:13.340
So the fluorinated chemicals
that have been studied,

00:54:13.340 --> 00:54:15.300
there's vast numbers
of animal studies,

00:54:15.300 --> 00:54:20.180
and then inadvertently, the very
sad, quote, human studies where

00:54:20.180 --> 00:54:23.050
human populations are exposed
and you find human health

00:54:23.050 --> 00:54:23.930
problems.

00:54:23.930 --> 00:54:27.890
So I think the harm
from C8 is known.

00:54:27.890 --> 00:54:31.220
From C6, there are 40 kinds.

00:54:31.220 --> 00:54:34.010
It's going to be really
hard to prove things.

00:54:34.010 --> 00:54:37.390
The fact that it ends up in
the brain is not a good sign.

00:54:37.390 --> 00:54:38.844
And they are
biologically active.

