products is a high goal.

00:55:17.720 --> 00:55:20.530
But it feels to me
just like Annapurna.

00:55:20.530 --> 00:55:24.010
That seemed pretty impossible,
one of the world's highest

00:55:24.010 --> 00:55:26.200
mountain that had
never been climbed

00:55:26.200 --> 00:55:27.720
by a woman or an American.

00:55:27.720 --> 00:55:31.720
But we were able to get
the team together and reach

00:55:31.720 --> 00:55:32.890
the summit of Annapurna.

00:55:32.890 --> 00:55:36.080
And so to me, this
feels just the same.

00:55:36.080 --> 00:55:37.510
A great team.

00:55:37.510 --> 00:55:40.200
If you sign our mailing list,
you'll be part of the team,

00:55:40.200 --> 00:55:44.450
working with scientists, people
in industry, government, NGOs.

00:55:44.450 --> 00:55:46.025
And we all see the same summit.

00:55:46.025 --> 00:55:48.050
It's a healthier world.

00:55:48.050 --> 00:55:53.160
And I think moving step by step,
we can all achieve that goal.

